title: #IDKMYDE - The Rebellion Of Nat Turner

description:
The Black Effect Presents... I Didn't Know Maybe You Didn't Either.

In this episode of I Didn’t Know Maybe You Didn’t Either we take a look back at the slave revolt Nat Turner started in 1831 and the price he paid for it.
